quot%3BAnd%20you%20can't%20not%20clear%20a%20tunnel%20if%20there's%20a%20potential%20for%20a%20hostage%20to%20be%20in%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20claimed%20in%202021%20to%20have%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fbreaking-news%2Fhamass-sinwar-we-have-10000-terrorists-within-israel-669265%5C%22%3E300%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20tunnels%20underneath%20Gaza%2C%20a%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20enclave%20that's%20roughly%20140%20square%20miles%20and%20home%20to%20around%202%20million%20people.%20Israel%20has%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.il%2Fen%2FDepartments%2FGeneral%2Foperation-guardian-of-the-walls-10-may-2021%5C%22%3Ereferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20subterranean%20network%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmetro%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Ba%20vast%20underground%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20its%20sheer%20size%20and%20depth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Fmini-sites%2Fthe-hamas-terrorist-organization%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-hamas-underground-city-of-terror%2F%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20tunnels%20are%20used%20to%20hide%20and%20store%20collections%20of%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%2C%20function%20as%20command%20centers%20and%20bunkers%2C%20and%20allow%20for%20the%20hidden%20movement%20and%20smuggling%20of%20militants%20and%20weapons%20both%20underneath%20Gaza%20and%20also%20into%20Israel.%20Access%20points%2C%20the%20military%20adds%2C%20are%20hidden%20inside%20places%20like%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20other%20civilian%20buildings.%20Israel%20has%20also%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20spending%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20construct%20its%20subterranean%20network%20and%20of%20diverting%20construction%20materials%20to%20the%20tunnels%20that%20could%20otherwise%20be%20used%20to%20build%20civilian%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20fighter%20from%20Izz%20al-Din%20al-Qassam%2