idney-powell-be-disbarred-for-election-lawsuits-conspiracy-theories-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3E2020%20election%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Powell%20could%20be%20in%20legal%20jeopardy%20for%20carrying%20water%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20he%20only%20lost%20to%20Biden%20because%20of%20a%20complex%2C%20multi-state%20conspiracy%20to%20change%20votes%20or%20enable%20massive%20voter%20fraud.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lawyers-sanctioned-by-courts-election-lawsuits-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EPowell%20was%20sanctioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Wisconsin%20officials%20unsuccessfully%20sought%20a%20similar%20penalty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETexas%20bar%20officials%20have%20tried%20to%20yank%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsidney-powell-avoids-disbarment-texas-judge-tosses-misnumbered-exhibits-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EPowell's%20law%20license%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20before.%20But%20University%20of%20Houston%20Law%20Center%20legal%20ethicist%20Renee%20Knake%20Jefferson%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegalethics.substack.com%2Fp%2Flegal-ethics-sidney-powell-guilty-election-trump%3Futm_source%3Dprofile%26utm_medium%3Dreader2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20guilty%20plea%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20basis%20for%20disbarment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3ETexas%20is%20going%20after%20Sidney%20Powell's%20license%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAttorney%20ethics%20rules%20in%20Texas%20require%20disbarment%20for%20%26quot%3Bserious%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20category%20that%20includes%20%26quot%3Bany%20misdemeanor%20involving%20theft%2C%20embezzlement%2C%20or%20fraudulent%20or%20reckless%20misappropriation%20of%20money%20or%20other%20property%3B%20or%20any%20attempt%2C%20conspiracy%2C%20or%20solicitation%20of%20another%20to%20commit%26quot%3B%20such%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBennett%2C%20the%20disciplinary%20lawyer%2C%20said%20he%20has%20kept%20tabs%20on%20Powell%20for%20years%20because%20both%20of%20them%20worked%20in%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Western%20District%20of%20Texas%20decades%20ago.%20He%20thinks%20it's%20time%20for%20her%20to%20stop%20practicing%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can't%20disbar%20somebody%20like%20Sidney%20Powell%2C%20who%20are%20you%20disbarring%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClaire%20Reynolds%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20the%20Texas%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Disciplinary%20Counsel%2C%20said%20the%20Georgia%20case%20shouldn't%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20pending%20effort%20to%20disbar%20Powell.%20But%20she%20was%20mum%20on%20whether%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20new%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20required%20by%20statute%20to%20keep%20all%20pending%20disciplinary%20matters%20confidential%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20even%20be%20able%20to%20confirm%20whether%20anything%20was%20pending%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EPowell's%20%26quot%3BDefending%20the%20Republic%26quot%3B%20has%20raised%20over%20%2417%20million%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20could%20take%20months%20or%20years%20for%20bar%20officials%20to%20go%20after%20Powell's%20law%20license.%20Since%20she%20went%20to%20work%20on%20behalf%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20supporters%2C%20she%20appears%20to%20have%20done%20little%20else%3B%20based%20on%20a%20docket%20search%20for%20her%20name%20using%20Westlaw%2C%20her%20last%20appearance%20in%20federal%20court%20as%20a%20lawyer%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20an%20effort%20to%20avoid%20sanctions%20in%20the%20Wisconsin%20case%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe's%20involved%20in%20many%20other%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20not%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20but%20as%20a%20defendant.%20Smartmatic%20and%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems%2C%20both%20voting%20technology%20companies%2C%20have%20sued%20her%20for%20defamation%2C%20claiming%20that%20she%20and%20other%20Trump%20supporters%20devastated%20their%20business%20by%20falsely%20claiming%20that%20they%20helped%20rig%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20she's%20running%20a%20nonprofit%20with%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20in%20the%20bank%20that%20has%20paid%20her%20%24120%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20rent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsidney-powell-defending-the-republic-fund-january-6-capitol-riot-criminal-defense-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EPowell%20runs%20Defending%20the%20Republic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20a%20political%20nonprofit%20that%20doesn't%20have%20to%20disclose%20its%20donors.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20in%202021%20that%20it%20had%20raised%20over%20%2414%20million%3B%20its%20tax%20return%20for%20the%20year%20ending%20in%20November%202021%20states%20that%20it%20raised%20nearly%20%2416.4%20million.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDonations%20fell%20sharply.%20According%20to%20its%202021%20tax%20return%2C%20which%20is%20on%20file%20in%20Florida%2C%20DTR%20only%20raised%20%241.1%20million%20that%20year.%20It%20spent%20nearly%20%244.5%20million%2C%20putting%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20its%20war%20chest.%20Still%2C%20the%20group%20had%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20on%20hand%20as%20of%20November%202022%2C%20the%20filings%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20group%20has%20spent%20millions%20on%20legal%20fee