%20%E2%80%94John%20Spencer%20(%40SpencerGuard)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1714817201436520835%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20explosive%20is%20distinct-looking%2C%20featuring%20a%20concave%2C%20shallow%20disc%20that%20rests%20on%20a%20smaller%20bomb.%20EFP%20IEDs%20are%20just%20one%20type%20of%20improvised%20device%2C%20but%20the%20weapon%20gained%20notoriety%20for%20its%20range%2C%20destructive%20potential%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20inflict%20severe%20damage%20on%20both%20vehicles%20and%20personnel%2C%20as%20it%20did%20to%20US%20forces%20during%20the%20Iraq%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captured%20cache%20of%20Hamas%20weaponry%20indicates%20the%20group%20either%20made%20its%20own%20or%20acquired%20them%20from%20an%20external%20actor%2C%20such%20as%20Iran.%20Beyond%20bringing%20them%20into%20Israel%20during%20their%20bloody%20assault%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20it%20may%20have%20a%20larger%20stockpile%20for%20future%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222227%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20troop%20looking%20at%20copper%20plates%20for%20EFPs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65318844be9edfa8eda534e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223207%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldier%20examining%20copper%20plates%20for%20EFPs%20in%20Iraq.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEFPs%20are%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20roadside%20IEDs%20made%20of%20machined%20copper%20placed%20into%20a%20variety%20of%20cheap%2C%20everyday%20objects%2C%20like%20coffee%20cans%2C%20jars%2C%20or%20kitchen%20pots.%20They've%20seen%20frequent%20use%20by%20militias%2C%20terrorists%2C%20and%20guerilla%20forces%20and%20are%20typically%20employed%20as%20asymmetric%20weapons%20against%20larger%20and%20more%20formidable%20targets.%20Iranian-backed%20Shiite%20militias%20used%20them%20during%20the%20war%20in%20Iraq%20following%20the%202003%20US%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Iranian%20Gen.%20Qassem%20Soleimani%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20Quds%20Force%20commander%20who%20the%20US%20eliminated%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20nearly%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fnation-world%2Fsoleimanis-legacy-the-gruesome-high-tech-ieds-that-haunted-u-s-troops-in-iraq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfamously%20armed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Iraqi%20militias%20with%20EFPs%20and%20trained%20them%20on%20the%20Iranian-engineered%20devices.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20his%20assassination%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdod-says-us-military-killed-top-iranian-general-qasem-soleimani-2020-1%5C%22%3Eblamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20and%20the%20Quds%20Force%20for%20the%20death%20of%20American%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20activated%2C%20the%20compact%20explosives%20inside%20the%20object%20fire%20the%20copper%20disc%20upwards%2C%20effectively%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20hot%2C%20high-speed%2C%20high-velocity%20munition.%20That%20copper%20projectile%2C%20once%20heated%20by%20explosives%2C%20is%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bslug%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20rapid%20motion%20out%20towards%20the%20target.%20While%20it%20can%20deal%20damage%20over%20a%20few%20dozen%20meters%2C%20EFPs%20are%20far%20more%20accurate%C2%A0and%20destructive%20at%20close%20range%20or%20directly%20beneath%20a%20target%2C%20like%20US%20troops%20saw%20in%20Iraq.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20US'%20invasion%2C%20troops%20reported%20that%20among%20the%20IEDs%20they%20faced%2C%20the%20EFPs%20were%20far%20deadlier%20and%20more%20effective%20than%20other%20roadside%20bombs%20or%20explosives%20they'd%20encountered.%20Soldiers%20said%20EFPs%2C%20hidden%20in%20foam%20blocks%20imitating%20street%20curbs%20and%20rocks%2C%20ripped%20through%20vehicles%20driving%20along%20dirt%20roads%2C%20with%20shards%20of%20the%20copper%20slug%20shredding%20armor%20and%20bodies%20at%20incredible%20speeds.%20One%20former%20Air%20Force%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2Fsoleimanis-legacy-gruesome-high-tech-ieds-that-haunted-us-troops-iraq%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20they%20were%20the%20worst%20explosive%20device%20he%20encountered%20during%20his%20time%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statistics%20match%20the%20EFPs'%20deadly%20reputation%2C%20too.%20The%20explosives%20killed%20at%20least%20196%20US%20troops%20and%20wounded%20nearly%20900%20between%202005%20and%202011%2C%20defense%20officials%20said%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20challenge%20with%20EFPs%2C%20like%20other%20IEDs%2C%20is%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20locate%20or%20spot%20them%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late%2C%C2%A0given%20they%20may%20look%20like%20ordinary%20objects.%20Another%20challenge%20is%20that%20EFP%20makers%20could%20easily%20change%20the%20bombs'%20designs%20to%20bypass%20American%20vehicle%20countermeasures%20and%20ensure%20the%20slugs%20hit%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20attitude%20and%20approach%20to%20combat%20in%20Iraq%C2%A0likely%20played%20a%20role%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BWe%20honestly%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20these%20guys%20were%20capable%20of%20doing%20this%20kind%20of%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20senior%20defense%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwp-dyn%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F2007%2F09%2F30%2FAR2007093001675_5.html%3Fsid%3DST2007092900754%26itid%3Dlk_inline_manual_29%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202007.%20%26quot%3BWe%20underestimated%20them.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20vehicle%20wrecked%20by%20IEDs%2C%20Iraq.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65318898be9edfa8eda5355e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20remains%20of%20an%20American%20Humvee%2C%20one%20of%20four%20that%20were%20disable%20by%20massive%20IEDs%2C%20lies%20on%20a%20dirt%20road%20on%20August%204%2C%202007%2C%20in%20Hawr%20Rajab%2C%20Iraq.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Lowy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20weapons%20are%20a%20part%20of%20Hamas'%20arsenal%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20they'd%20be%20used%20in%20Gaza%20to%20fend%20off%20an%20invasion%2C%20as%20urban%20combat%20lends%20itself%20to%20tricks%20and%20traps.%20That%20could%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20IDF%20troops%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gearing-up-ground-invasion-war-with-hamas-risks-expanding-2023-10%5C%22%3Eground%20offensive%20in%20the%20strip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%20noted%20that%20Israel%20likely%20would%20not%20be%20unprepared%20for%20these%20threats%2C%20writing%20that%20the%20IDF%20%26quot%3Bwill%20face%20this%20threat%20and%20other%20IEDs%20with%20years%20of%20their%20own%20lessons%20learned%26quot%3B%20and%20countermeasures%20pulled%20from%20past%20fights%2C%20including%20against%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Hamas%20executed%20its%20surprise%20terror%20attacks%2C%20which%20killed%20at%20least%201%2C300%20people%20and%20injured%20over%204%2C000%20more%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20has%20repeatedly%20signaled%20it%20intends%20to%20launch%20a%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%2C%20a%20densely%20packed%20urban%20area%20home%20to%20over%202%20million%20people%2C%C2%A0as%20its%20jets%20bombed%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-air-force-photos-fighter-aircraft-armed-unguided-weapons-2023-10%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20airstrikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20destroyed%20whole%20areas%2C%20killing%20over%203%2C000%20Palestinians%20