Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani's%20claim%20is%20still%20a%20setback%20for%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20whom%20the%20BJP%20wants%20suspended%20from%20parliament.%20The%20allegation%20that%20she%20handed%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%2C%20if%20proved%2C%20could%20comprise%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%20that%20could%20bring%20a%20suspension%20order%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECaught%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-questions%26quot%3B%20controversy%20swirling%20around%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20said%20he%20was%20filing%20the%20affidavit%20since%20the%20matter%20involves%20him%20and%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20controversy%20roping%20in%20the%20Parliamentary%20Privilege%20Committee%20and%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra%20thought%20the%20only%20way%20to%20attack%20PM%20Modi%20was%20by%20attacking%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20and%20so%20she%20%26quot%3Bexpected%20support%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20affidavit%20read.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20shared%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20so%20he%20could%20frame%20the%20questions%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20said.%20He%20went%20along%20with%20the%20idea%20because%20he%20thought%20through%20her%2C%20he%20would%20get%20support%20in%20the%20Opposition-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20received%20support%20from%20others%20in%20this%20effort%2C%20including%20journalists%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20and%20former%20Adani%20Group%20employees%2C%20who%20fed%20her%20unverified%20information.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20he%20named%20Sucheta%20Dalal%20--%20who%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20--%20and%20a%20few%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani%20also%20claimed%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20was%20also%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdominating%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bambitious%26quot%3B%20person%20who%20also%20made%20a%20number%20of%20demands%20for%20%26quot%3Bvarious%20favours%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20met%20to%20retain%20her%20support%20and%20their%20close%20friendship.%20The%20list%20included%20gifting%20her%20expensive%20luxury%20items%2C%20%26quot%3Bproviding%20support%20for%20renovation%20of%20her%20officially%20allotted%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%2C%20travel%20expenses%2C%20holidays%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20ill%20afford%20to%20displease%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20read.%20%26quot%3BMany%20a%20time%20I%20felt%20she%20was%20taking%20undue%20advantage%20of%20me%20and%20pressurising%20me%20to%20do%20things%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20choice%2C%20because%20of%20aforementioned%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20demanded%20immediate%20suspension%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20alleging%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Btook%20bribes%20to%20ask%20questions%26quot%3B%20in%20parliament%20from%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20target%20his%20business%20rival%2C%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20and%20PM%20Modi.%20Mr%20Dubey%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20accusing%20Ms%20Moitra%20of%20breach%20of%20parliamentary%20privilege%2C%20contempt%20of%20House%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hiranandani%20Group%20had%20lost%20energy%20and%20infra%20contract%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Ms%20Moitra's%20questions%20were%20directed%20at%20perpetuating%20the%20business%20interests%20of%20the%20former%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20alleged%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20complaint%20has%20been%20referred%20by%20the%20Speaker%20to%20parliament's%20Ethics%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20junior%20Union%20minister%20for%20Information%20Technology%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20controversy%20and%20indicating%20Mr%20Hiranandani's%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%20that%20this%20company%20was%20actively%20and%20aggressively%20lobbying%20for%20Data%20