%20out%20on%20him%20as%20he%20was%20spotted%20and%20captured%20by%20security%20personnel%20who%20called%20the%20police.%C2%A0It%20is%20already%20known%20that%20the%2022-year-old%20has%20also%20committed%20thefts%20and%20burglaries%20in%20another%20gallery%2C%20where%2C%20after%20its%20closure%2C%20he%20took%20money%20from%20several%20cash%20registers%20and%20tried%20to%20steal%20other%20items%2C''%20the%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20custody%20for%20three%20months%20and%20could%20face%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20prison%20if%20convicted%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F19%2Fman-who-pretended-to-be-mannequin-in-warsaw-shop-window-charged-with-theft%5C%22%3EGuardian.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20similar%20incident%2C%20police%20say%20he%20dined%20late%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20a%20second%20shopping%20center%20and%20waited%20for%20it%20to%20close.%20He%C2%A0entered%20a%20clothing%20store%20and%20''exchanged%20his%20clothes%20for%20new%20ones''%2C%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20restaurant%20for%20another%20meal.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20caught%20on%20CCT%20V%20slipping%20under%20the%20clothing%20store's%20partially%20open%20shutters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20were%20amused%20by%20the%20stunt%20and%20posted%20hilarious%20comments.%20''One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Well%20he%20wood%20be.%20Wooden%20he%2C''%20while%20another%20commented%2C%20''This%20is%20hilarious.''%20A%20third%20said%2C%20''Question%3A%20what's%20the%20most%20Polish%20burglary%20you've%20ever%20heard%3F%20Answer%3A%C2%A0A%20man%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20posing%20as%20a%20mannequin%20in%20a%20Warsaw%20shop%20window%20to%20steal%20jewellery%20after%20closing%20time.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Crime%20is%20bad%2C%20obviously%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20give%20this%20guy%20some%20credit%20for%20creativity%20and%20balls.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697738160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fin761epo_-mannequin_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthief-in-poland-poses-as-mannequin-before-stealing-jewellery-from-mall-arrested-4497996%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20staff%20and%20shoppers%20failed%20to%20notice%20anything%20suspicious%20as%20the%20man%20blended%20in%20with%20the%20mannequins%20in%20the%20window.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthief-in-poland-poses-as-mannequin-before-stealing-jewellery-from-mall-arrested-4497996%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthief-in-poland-poses-as-mannequin-before-stealing-jewellery-from-mall-arrested-4497996%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthief-in-poland-poses-as-mannequin-before-stealing-jewellery-from-mall-arrested-4497996%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ITC%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20up%206%25%20at%20Rs%204.8K%20cr%2C%20rural%20green%20shoots%20visible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697737870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F24%2Ffull%2F1690210479-7699.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fitc-q2fy24-results-profit-after-tax-up-6-02-at-rs-4-898-07-crore-123101901328_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Says%20public%20investment%20strong%2C%20consumption%20demand%20relatively%20subdued%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fitc-q2fy24-results-profit-after-tax-up-6-02-at-rs-4-898-07-crore-123101901328_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproje