ors%20and%20smart%20people%20are%20looking%20at%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Barkat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20while%20Israel%20has%20waged%20many%20wars%20through%20its%20history%2C%20the%20economy%20has%20remained%20strong%20and%20resilient%2C%20weathering%20the%20storms%20and%20coming%20out%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20he%20was%20eager%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20exception%20to%20the%20rule%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20he%20sees%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20his%20country%20even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20Mr%20Barkat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20opportunities%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20reduced.%20They're%20only%20going%20to%20increase%20because%20Israel%20is%20going%20to%20be%20an%20even%20safer%20place%20(after%20war%20ends%20and%20the%20country%20prevails)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20government's%20pledge%20to%20eradicate%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20terror%20group%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20he%20has%20personally%20witnessed%20growing%20international%20interest%20in%20Israel%20as%20a%20potential%20investment%20destination.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20trips%20I've%20made%2C%20including%20to%20India%20not%20long%20ago%2C%20this%20year%2C%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20the%20world%20to%20stand%20with%20Israel%20in%20the%20war%20with%20Hamas%20and%20%26quot%3Bcollaborate%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20country%2C%20Barkat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20recommend%20the%20world%20unite%20with%20us%20against%20Hamas%2C%20comes%20together%20with%20us%20against%20Iran%20and%20Kzbaah%20and%20collaborate%20with%20us%20on%20taking%20our%20economy%20forward%20because%20we%20know%20how%20to%20create%20win-win%20global%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20time%20to%20invest%20is%20before