mpany.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EOnePlus%20Open%20specifications%2C%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dual-SIM%20(Nano)%20OnePlus%20Open%20is%20a%20foldable%20phone%20that%20runs%20on%20OxygenOS%2013.2%20based%20on%20Android%2013%20out-of-the-box.%20It%20sports%20a%207.82-inch%20(2%2C268x2%2C440%C2%A0pixels)%202K%20Flexi-fluid%20LTPO%203.0%20AMOLED%20display%20with%20a%201-120Hz%20dynamic%20refresh%20rate%2C%20a%20240Hz%20touch%20response%20rate%2C%20and%20up%20to%202%2C800%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness.%20The%20display%20has%20an%20Ultra%20Thin%20Glass%20protective%20material%20and%20supports%201%2C440Hz%20pulse-width%20modulation%20(PWM)%20dimming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outer%20screen%20of%20the%20OnePlus%20Open%20is%20a%206.31-inch%20(1%2C116x2%2C484%20pixels)%202K%20LTPO%203.0%20Super%20Fluid%20AMOLED%20display%20with%20a%2010-120Hz%20dynamic%20refresh%20rate%2C%20a%20240Hz%20touch%20response%20rate%2C%20and%20up%20to%202%2C800%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness.%20It%20has%20a%20ceramic%20guard%20protective%20material%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20Both%20displays%20are%C2%A0T%C3%9CV%20Rheinland%20Intelligent%20Eye%20Care%20certified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20data-dimension%3D%5C%221200x800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22oneplus%20open%20ui%20oneplus%20open%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Foneplus_open_ui_1697722884742.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnePlus%20Open%20runs%20on%20Android%2013-based%20OxygenOS%2013.2%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnePlus%20has%20equipped%20the%20foldable%20handset%20with%20Qualcomm's%20Snapdragon%208%20Gen%202%20chip%20with%20an%20Adreno%20740%20GPU%2C%20paired%20with%2016GB%20of%20LPDDR5x%20RAM.%20The%20company%20says%20that%20available%20memory%20on%20the%20smartphone%20can%20be%20expanded%20in%20increments%20of%204GB%2C%208GB%2C%20and%2012GB%20by%20utilising%20unused%20storage%20on%20the%20handset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20the%20OnePlus%20has%20a%20Hasselblad-branded%20triple%20camera%20setup.%20It%20has%20a%2048-megapixel%20primary%20camera%20with%20a%201%2F1.43-inch%C2%A0Sony%20LYT-T808%20%E2%80%9CPixel%20Stacked%E2%80%9D%C2%A0CMOS%20sensor%20with%20optical%20image%20stabilisation%20(OIS)%20and%20electronic%20image%20stabilisation%20(EIS)%2C%20an%2085-degree%20field-of-view%20and%20an%20f%2F1.7%20aperture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20OnePlus%20Open%20is%20also%20equipped%20with%20a%2064-megapixel%20telephoto%20camera%20with%20an%C2%A0OmniVision%20OV64B%20sensor%20with%20OIS%2C%20EIS%2C%20a%2033.4-degree%20field-of-view%2C%20and%20an%20f%2F2.6%20aperture.%20It%20supports%203x%20optical%20zoom%2C%206x%20in-sensor%20zoom%2C%20and%20up%20to%20120x%20digital%20zoom.%20It%20also%20features%20a%2048-megapixel%20ultra-wide-angle%20camera%20(that%20doubles%20as%20a%20macro%20camera)%20with%20a%20Sony%20IMX581%20sensor%20with%20EIS%2C%20a%20114-degree%20field-of-view%2C%20and%20an%20f%2F2.2%20aperture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20inner%20display%20of%20the%20OnePlus%20Open%2C%20you%20get%20a%2020-megapixel%20primary%20camera%20with%20EIS%20and%2091-degree%20field-of-view%20and%20an%20f%2F2.2%20aperture.%20The%20foldable%20phone%20is%20also%20equipped%20with%20a%2032-megapixel%20camera%20on%20the%20outer%20screen%20with%20EIS%20and%20an%2088.5-degree%20field%20of%20view%20and%20an%20f%2F2.4%20aperture%2C%20for%20selfies%20and%20video%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20OnePlus%20Open%20is%20equipped%20with%20512GB%20of%20UFS%204.0%20storage.%20Connectivity%20options%20on%20the%20handset%C2%A0include%205G%2C%204G%20LTE%2C%20Wi-Fi%207%2C%20Bluetooth%205.3%2C%20GPS%2F%20A-GPS%2C%20NFC%2C%20Beidou%2C%20GPS%2C%20GLONASS%2C%20Galileo%2C%20QZSS%20and%20a%20USB%20Type-C%20port%20with%20USB%203.1%20connectivity.%C2%A0It%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20sensors%20including%20an%20accelerometer%2C%20gyroscope%2C%20proximity%20sensor%2C%20sensor%20core%2C%20e-compass%2C%20flick-detect%20sensor%2C%20an