and%20war%20and%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20negotiations%20and%20diplomacy%20so%20that%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20fulfilled%20and%20the%20security%20concerns%20of%20Israel%20are%20also%20ensured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20had%20condemned%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20But%2C%20unlike%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20also%20explicitly%20condemned%20the%20attacks%20by%20Israeli%20military%20forces%20on%20civilian%20areas%20in%20Gaza.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Congress%20statement%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attribute%20the%20Gaza%20hospital%20strike%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697727020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F07211643%2F13024011.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShared%20our%20deep%20concern%20at%20the%20terrorism%2C%20violence%20and%20deteriorating%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%20Reiterated%20India's%20long-standing%20principled%20position%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Daily%20Despatch%3A%20Biden's%20Historic%20Israel%20Visit%2C%20Protests%20In%20Arab%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs4k1tsno_biden-netanyahu-daily-despatch_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20frontlines%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20NDTV%20brings%20you%20daily%20despatches%20by%20journalist%20Allan%20Sorensen%2C%20Middle%20East%20Correspondent%20for%20Danish%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad%2C%20giving%20insights%20and%20gripping%20first-hand%20accounts%20from%20the%20war-torn%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20on%20Air%20Force%20One%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20began%20a%20seven-hour%20visit%20in%20Israel%20sharing%20a%20big%20hug%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20arrived%20in%20Israel%20to%20express%20his%20support%20in%20the%20nation's%20current%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20During%20his%20brief%20visit%2C%20he%20held%20talks%20with%20Netanyahu%2C%20took%20part%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%2C%20and%20met%20with%20a%20few%20of%20the%20relatives%20of%20some%20203%20Israeli%20and%20foreign%20hostages%20kept%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Biden's%20visit%20is%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20gesture%20of%20support%20for%20Israel's%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%2C%20it%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20to%20refrain%20from%20attacking%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20supportive%20remark%2C%20President%20Biden%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20the%20United%20States%20stands%20-%20and%20we%20will%20stand%20forever%20-%20we%20will%20not%20let%20you%20ever%20be%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20also%20drew%20a%20comparison%20to%20the%20Holocaust%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20rationalizing%20it%2C%20no%20excusing%20it.%20Period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20brutality%20we%20saw%20would%20have%20cut%20deep%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20it%20cuts%20deeper%20here%20in%20Israel.%20October%207%2C%20which%20was%20a%20sacred%20to%20-%20a%20sacred%20Jewish%20holiday%2C%20became%20the%20deadliest%20day%20for%20the%20Jewish%20people%20since%20the%20Holocaust.%20It%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20surface%20painful%20memories%20and%20scars%20left%20by%20millennia%20of%20antisemitism%20and%20the%20genocide%20of%20the%20Jewish%20people.%20The%20world%20watched%20then%2C%20it%20knew%2C%20and%20the%20world%20did%20nothing.%20We%20will%20not%20stand%20by%20and%20do%20nothing%20again.%20Not%20today%2C%20not%20tomorrow%2C%20not%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20repeated%20his%20warning%20to%20Hamas'%20regional%20backers%20Hezbollah%20and%20Iran%2C%20but%20also%20urged%20Israel%20to%20not%20make%20the%20same%20mistakes%20as%20the%20US%20after%20the%209%2F11%20al%20Qaeda%20terror%20attacks%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20nation%20the%20size%20of%20Israel%2C%20it%20was%20like%2015%209%2F11s.%20The%20scale%20may%20be%20different%2C%20but%20I'm%20sure%20those%20horrors%20have%20tapped%20into%20some%20kind%20of%20primal%20feeling%20in%20Israel%2C%20just%20like%20it%20did%20and%20felt%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20look%20at%20what%20has%20happened%20here%20to%20your%20mothers%2C%20your%20fathers%2C%20your%20grandparents%2C%20sons%2C%20daughters%2C%20children%20-%20even%20babies%20-%20and%20not%20scream%20out%20for%20justice.%20Justice%20must%20be%20done.%20But%20I%20caution%20this%3A%20While%20you%20feel%20that%20rage%2C%20don't%20be%20consumed%20by%20it.%20After%209%2F11%2C%20we%20were%20enraged%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20And%20while%20we%20sought%20justice%20and%20got%20justice%2C%20we%20also%20made%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israeli%20media%2C%20Biden%20also%20asked%20Israel%20to%20ease%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20civilian%20population%20in%20Gaza%20by%20allowing%20truckloads%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20enter.%20Late%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20Egypt%20announced%20that%2020%20trucks%20in%20the%20massive%20humanitarian%20convoy%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20border%20were%20cleared%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20went%20to%20historic%20lengths%20to%20oppose%20the%20claims%20of%20Hamas%20on%20the%20explosion%20at%20the%20al-Ahli%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Israel's%20history%2C%20a%20secret%20recording%20by%20the%20army%20intelligence%20unit%208200%20was%20cleared%20for%20publishing.%20The%20recording%20is%20a%20conversation%20between%20two%20Hamas%20members%20immediately%20after%20the%20explosion%20at%20the%20hospital.%20They%20can%20be%20heard%20explaining%20the%20explosion%20and%20concluding%20that%20it%20must%20be%20due%20to%20a%20misfired%20Palestinian%20rocket.%20In%20addition%2C%20Israeli%20security%20cameras%20caught%20the%20explosion%2C%20showing%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20fired%20against%20the%20Tel%20Aviv%20area%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20rockets%20landed%20near%20the%20hospital%20and%20caused%20an%20explosion.%20Qatari%20TV%20station%20al%20Jazeera%20also%20filmed%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20planned%20meeting%20between%20Biden%20and%20three%20Arab%20leaders%20in%20Jordan%20was%20canceled%20after%20the%20Gaza%20hospital%20attack%2C%20blamed%20on%20Israel%20throughout%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20filled%20the%20streets%20in%20Ramallah%2C%20Amman%20and%20Beirut%20in%20rage%20against%20Israel%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20President%20canceled%20the%20meeting%20with%20Biden.%20According%20to%20US%20sources%2C%20this%20meeting%20was%20planned%20to%20start%20dealing%20with%20the%20future%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20after%20an%20Israeli%20land%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20war%20cabinet%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20enter%20the%20next%20stage%20of%20the%20war%20against%20Hamas.%20This%20is%20according%20to%20Israeli%20army%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari.%20The%20decision%20is%20widely%20understood%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20northern%20border%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%2C%20sporadic%20and%20mutual%20attacks%20continued%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20Hezbollah%20fired%20at%20least%20six%20anti-tank%20missiles%20against%20Israeli%20targets%2C%20hitting%20and%20wounding%20at%20least%20one%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20latest%20escalations%20on%20the%20northern%20border%2C%20the%20Hezbollah%20also%20fired%20nine%20rockets%20against%20the%20city%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%20Israel%20retaliated%20to%20this%20attack%20by%20hitting%20Hezbollah%20targets%20inside%20Lebanon.%20This%20time%2C%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Tyre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lebanese%20media%20al-Mayadeen%2C%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20targeted%20a%20monument%20of%20former%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20Quds%20Force%20commander%20Qasem%20Soleimani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20regional%20development%2C%20Israel's%20National%20Security%20Council%20issued%20a%20warning%20against%20travel%20to%20Turkey%20and%20Morocco.%20The%20Israeli%20authorities%20fear%20that%20Israeli%20travelers%20will%20be%20targets%20due%20to%20the%20current%20tension%20around%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Security%20Council%20raised%20the%20alert%20to%20Turkey%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20four%20and%20called%20on%20all%20Israelis%20in%20the%20country%20to%20leave%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Tunisia%20a%20historic%20synagogue%20was%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20amid%20mass%20rioting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20people%20were%20filmed%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20synagogue%20in%20the%20central%20Tunisian%20city%20of%20Al%20Hammah.%20Videos%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20people%20attacking%20the%20synagogue%20without%20any%20intervention%20from%20Tunesian%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697726580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs4k1tsno_biden-netanyahu-daily-despatch_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-bidens-historic-israel-visit-protests-in-arab-world-4497425%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20arriving%20on%20Air%20Force%20One%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20began%20a%20seven-hour%20visit%20in%20Israel%20sharing%20a%20big%20hug%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-bidens-historic-israel-visit-protests-in-arab-world-4497425%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Orionid%20Meteor%20Shower%20To%20Dazzle%20The%20Night%20Sky%20On%20October%2021-22%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20the%20Americas%20witnessed%20the%20'Ring%20of%20Fire'%20Solar%20Eclipse%20last%20week%2C%20another%20celestial%20event%20is%20set%20to%20delight%20skygazers.%20The%20Orionids%20meteor%20shower%20will%20peak%20this%20weekend%2C%20providing%20people%20to%20witness%20one%20of%20the%20most%20spectacular%20events%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Orionid%20meteor%20shower%2C%20an%20annual%20phenomenon%20that%20lights%20up%20the%20night%20sky%20every%20October%2C%20is%20produced%20when%20Earth%20passes%20through%20the%20debris%20left%20behind%20by%20Halley's%20Comet.%20Though%20this%20shower%20lasts%20until%20November%2022%2C%20it%20will%20peak%20on%20Friday%20and%20Saturday%20(October%2020-21)%20over%20the%20northern%20hemisphere%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2F34373-orionid-meteor-shower-guide.html%5C%22%3ESpace.com.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0The%20Orionids%20are%20visible%20to%20skywatchers%20in%20both%20the%20Northern%20and%20Southern%20Hemispheres%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20image%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENot%20only%20does%20October%20treat%20us%20to%20an%20eclipse%2C%20but%20we%20are%20in%20for%20what%20could%20be%20some%20spectacular%20meteor%20showers%20as%20well!%20For%20the%20stargazers%20out%20there%2C%20here's%20the%20rundown%3A%20October%2018th%20we'll%20see%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20%CE%B5-Geminid%20Meteor%20Shower%2C%20October%2021%20will%20be%20the%20apex%20of%20the%20Orionid%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwQ6ry4OzCU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwQ6ry4OzCU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Buzz%20Aldrin%20(%40TheRealBuzz)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheRealBuzz%2Fstatus%2F1714317966173511803%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Orionids%20get%20their%20name%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20meteors%20appear%20to%20originate%20around%20the%20Orion%20constellation.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsolarsystem.nasa.gov%2Fasteroids-comets-and-meteors%2Fmeteors-and-meteorites%2Fleonids%2Fin-depth%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Leonids%2520are%2520bright%2520meteors%2Csome%2520of%2520the%2520fastest%2520meteors.%5C%22%3ENASA%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Orionids%20zip%20through%20the%20sky%20at%2041%20miles%20(66%20kilometers)%20per%20second%2C%20only%203%20miles%20(5%20km)%20per%20second%20slower%20than%20the%20speedy%20Leonids.%C2%A0The%20sheer%20speed%20of%20the%20Orionids%20makes%20them%20unique%2C%20traveling%20at%20about%20148%2C000%20mph%20into%20Earth's%20atmosphere%2C%20according%20to%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20meteors%20come%20from%20leftover%20comet%20particles%20and%20bits%20from%20broken%20asteroids.%20A%20meteor%20shower%20occurs%20when%20the%20Earth%20crosses%20the%20path%20of%20a%20comet%20and%20collides%20with%20those%20particles%2C%20which%20burn%20up%20in%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EViewers%20with%20clear%20skies%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20about%2020%20meteors%20per%20hour%20during%20peak%20nights.%C2%A0This%20year%2C%20the%20moon%20will%20be%2037%25%20illuminated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20shower's%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPASS%20IT%20ON%3A%20The%20Orionid%20meteor%20shower%20peaks%20this%20coming%20Saturday%20night%20through%20early%20Sunday%20morning.%20Up%20to%2020%20meteors%20will%20be%20possible%20per%20hour!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMeteorShower%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MeteorShower%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSpace%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Space%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fbk9B6jvHDC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fbk9B6jvHDC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Mark%20Tarello%20(%40mark_tarello)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmark_tarello%2Fstatus%2F1713890914760888769%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Ch2%3EHow%20To%20See%20It%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20special%20equipment%20is%20needed%20to%20view%20the%20meteors%2C%20and%20our%20naked%20eyes%20are%20enough.%20As%20per%3Cem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnewsround%2F41691827%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20best%20place%20to%20see%20the%20Orionid%20meteor%20shower%20is%20somewhere%20dark%2C%20away%20from%20light%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Moon%20out%20of%20your%20line%20of%20sight.%20To%20prepare%2C%20you%20should%20let%20your%20eyes%20adjust%20to%20the%20dark%20by%20staying%20outside%20for%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20time%20to%20spot%20the%20meteors%20is%20between%20midnight%20and%20sunrise%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20October%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fr570oqlo_orionid-meteor-shower_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Forionid-meteor-shower-to-dazzle-the-night-sky-on-october-21-22-how-to-see-it-4497325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Orionid%20meteor%20shower%2C%20an%20annual%20phenomenon%20that%20lights%20up%20the%20night%20sky%20every%20October%2C%20is%20produced%20when%20Earth%20passes%20through%20the%20debris%20left%20behind%20by%20Halley's%20Comet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Forionid-meteor-shower-to-dazzle-the-night-sky-on-october-21-22-how-to-see-it-4497325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Forionid-meteor-shower-to-dazzle-the-night-sky-on-october-21-22-how-to-see-it-4497325%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Forionid-meteor-shower-to-dazzle-the-night-sky-on-october-21-22-how-to-see-it-4497325%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Why%20Does%20India%20Rank%20111%20Out%20of%20125%20Countries%20in%20Hunger%20Index%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19195213%2Fthumbnail-hunger-index.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20a%20country%20that%20ranks%20111%20out%20of%20125%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20%E2%80%98hunger%E2%80%99.%20According%20to%20the%20recently%20released%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20Report%202023%2C%20India%20performed%20worse%20than%20its%20neighbours.%20Only%20some%20of%20the%20very%20small%20nations%20of%20Africa%20were%20ranked%20worse%20off%20than%20India.%20The%20Indian%20government%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20report%2C%20saying%20its%20methodology%20was%20faulty.%20When%20we%20put%20those%20objections%20to%20the%20agencies%20which%20made%20the%20reports%2C%20they%20explained%20how%20the%20objections%20do%20not%20hold%20much%20water%2C%20and%20how%20out%20of%20all%20the%20countries%20ranked%2C%20only%20India%20had%20raised%20objections.%20Nonetheless%2C%20many%20other%20reports%20have%20also%20painted%20a%20poor%20picture%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20performance%20on%20various%20indicators%20of%20nutrition.%20Watch%20the%20full%20video%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20Banjot%20Kaur%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fqvh82sP4FhM%3Fsi%3DURLUo2S1uZrvKDn9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19195213%2Fthumbnail-hunger-index.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-india-111-out-of-125-countries-global-hunger-index%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire's%20Banjot%20Kaur%20explains%20why%2C%20despite%20being%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20India%20performs%20poorly%20on%20indicators%20of%20nutrition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-india-111-out-of-125-countries-global-hunger-index%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Teen%20Almost%20Dies%20After%20Eating%20Bacon%20And%20Egg%20Sandwich.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Australian%20woman%20is%20warning%20other%20parents%20about%20a%20cleaning%20tool%20for%20barbecues%20after%20her%20nine-year-old%20daughter%20almost%20died%20after%20eating%20a%20bacon%20and%20egg%20roll.%20Kristen%20Saunders%20from%20Newcastle%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20that%20her%20nine-year-old%20daughter%20was%20served%20the%20sandwich%20at%20a%20venue%20in%20July.%20Along%20with%20the%20food%2C%20she%20also%20swallowed%20a%20small%20wire-bristle%20from%20a%20barbecue%20brush.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20barbecue%20brush%20pierced%20her%20daughter's%20oesophagus%20and%20pushed%20into%20the%20carotid%20artery%20in%20her%20neck%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-10-17%2Fbarbecue-brush-warning-after-near-fatal-bacon-and-egg-roll-meal%2F102968758%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Saunders%20told%20ABC%20News%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20munching%20away%2C%20then%20she%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20she%20was%20choking.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20like%20most%20parents%2C%20we're%20we're%20like%2C%20'You'll%20be%20fine%2C%20have%20some%20water%2C%20it'll%20settle%20down'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20thought%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20doctor%20would%20resolve%20the%20problem.%20The%20visit%20revealed%20she%20had%20a%20high%20temperature.%20The%20girl%20struggled%20with%20a%20sore%20throat%20and%20had%20difficulty%20eating%20solid%20food.%20Her%20condition%20improved%20and%20even%20took%20part%20in%20the%20school%20athletics%20carnival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20symptoms%20started%20to%20appear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20this%20one%20particular%20day%20I%20was%20at%20home%20with%20her%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20she%20was%20a%20bit%20confused%20answering%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Saunders%20told%20the%20media%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Hang%20on%2C%20there's%20something%20really%20problematic%20here'%20and%20called%20the%20GP%20-%20she%20%5Bsaid%20to%5D%20go%20straight%20to%20the%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20was%20stumbling%2C%20disoriented%20and%20unable%20to%20recognise%20her%20family.%20%26quot%3BThey%20identified%20that%20there%20were%20some%20abscesses%20in%20the%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Saunders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20ended%20up%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20doing%20a%20CT%20and%20identified%20there%20was%20this%20tiny%20bit%20of%20wire%2C%20sort%20of%20near%20her%20neck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20flown%20to%20Westmead%20Children's%20Hospital%20in%20Sydney.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20day%20we%20realised%20it%20was%20pretty%20serious%20-%20there%20was%20a%20major%20infection%20in%20one%20of%20her%20arteries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20to%20replace%20it%20and%20there%20was%20a%20risk%20of%20all%20these%20different%20things%2C%20so%20that%20was%20pretty%20awful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20was%20successful%20and%20she%20had%20a%20phenomenal%20recovery.%20%26quot%3BShe%20actually%20had%20a%20phenomenal%20recovery%2C%20considering%20what%20it%20could%20have%20looked%20like%20and%20how%20it%20could%20have%20ended%20up%2C%20and%20she's%20doing%20really%20well%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Saunders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20off%20all%20her%20antibiotics%2C%20she's%20back%20to%20school%2C%20she'll%20be%20back%20to%20sport%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0220mbtg_kristen-saunders_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-teen-almost-dies-after-eating-bacon-and-egg-sandwich-heres-why-4497348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%209-year-old%20girl%20was%20left%20fighting%20for%20her%20life%20after%20she%20accidentally%20ate%20the%20bristle%20from%20a%20BBQ%20cleaning%20brush%20tucked%20inside%20a%20bacon%20and%20egg%20roll.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-teen-almost-dies-after-eating-bacon-and-egg-sandwich-heres-why-4497348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-teen-almost-dies-after-eating-bacon-and-egg-sandwich-heres-why-4497348%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-teen-almost-dies-after-eating-bacon-and-egg-sandwich-heres-why-4497348%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20says%20'those%20working%20from%20home%20are%20detached%20from%20reality'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104560406%2Cimgsize-33524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-says-those-working-from-home-are-detached-from-reality%2Farticleshow%2F104560431.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104560431.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20criticized%20the%20prevalence%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20stating%20that%20those%20working%20from%20home%20are%20%26quot%3Bdetached%20from%20reality.%26quot%3B%20He%20questioned%20the%20morality%20of%20allowing%20some%20people%20to%20work%20from%20home%20while%20others%2C%20such%20as%20factory%20workers%20and%20restaurant%20staff%2C%20had%20to%20continue%20working%20on-site.%20Musk%20had%20previously%20emailed%20Tesla%20workers%2C%20banning%20remote%20work%20unless%20personally%20approved%20by%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-says-those-working-from-home-are-detached-from-reality%2Farticleshow%2F104560431.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-says-those-working-from-home-are-detached-from-reality%2Famp_articleshow%2F104560431.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-says-those-working-from-home-are-detached-from-reality%2Famp_articleshow%2F104560431.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22French%20airports%20again%20hit%20by%20fake%20bomb%20threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104560452%2Cimgsize-1114750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrench-airports-again-hit-by-fake-bomb-threats%2Farticleshow%2F104560410.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104560410.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAt%20least%2014%20French%20airports%20received%20bomb%20threats%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20at%20least%20eight%20evacuated%2C%20in%20the%20latest%20series%20of%20false%20alarms%20that%20have%20rattled%20the%20country%20over%20the%20past%20week.%20Aviation%20authority%20DGAC%20confirmed%20the%20bomb%20threats%20without%20giving%20a%20precise%20number%2C%20while%20several%20airports%20put%20out%20social%20media%20messages%20about%20the%20evacuations%20and%20checks%20by%20security%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrench-airports-again-hit-by-fake-bomb-threats%2Farticleshow%2F104560410.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrench-airports-again-hit-by-fake-bomb-threats%2Famp_articleshow%2F104560410.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrench-airports-again-hit-by-fake-bomb-threats%2Famp_articleshow%2F104560410.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Advantage%20Ashok%20Gehlot%3F%20BJP%20Avoids%20Leadership%20Tussle%20In%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20are%20set%20for%20an%20intense%20battle%20for%20200%20seats%20when%20the%20state%20votes%20for%20a%20new%20government%20on%20November%2025.%20The%20BJP%20is%20looking%20at%20cashing%20in%20on%20anti-incumbency%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20banking%20on%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government's%20public%20outreach%20programmes.%20Both%20parties%20are%20steeped%20in%20internal%20conflicts%20and%20hope%20to%20play%20them%20to%20their%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20is%20known%20to%20vote%20in%20a%20new%20party%20every%20five%20years.%20Since%20the%201993%20mid-term%20assembly%20elections%2C%20no%20incumbent%20ruling%20party%20has%20been%20re-elected%20for%20a%20second%20straight%20term.%20If%20the%20trend%20continues%2C%20the%20BJP%20should%20be%20the%20beneficiary%20this%20time%2C%20after%20five%20years%20of%20Congress%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20focused%20on%20exploiting%20the%20rifts%20within%20the%20Congress%2C%20most%20prominently%20the%20open%20tussle%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Congress%20dissident%20Sachin%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20will%20come%20to%20power%20with%20over%20160%20seats%20as%20people%20have%20realised%20that%20the%20Congress'%20appeasement%20policy%20is%20against%20national%20interests.%20My%20personal%20view%20is%20that%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Congress%20high%20command%20are%20hardly%20visible%20as%20Gehlot%20is%20portraying%20it%20as%20his%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20former%20BJP%20MLA%20Shaitan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20has%20had%20many%20incidents%20of%20law-and-order%20breakdown%2C%20particularly%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Corruption%20cases%20like%20the%20infamous%20'red%20diary'%2C%20flashed%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20by%20a%20minister%20who%20was%20later%20dismissed%20by%20Gehlot%2C%20have%20become%20the%20talking%20points%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20election%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20despite%20corruption%20and%20law%20and%20order%20issues%2C%20Gehlot%20faces%20less%20anti-incumbency%20than%20anticipated.%20In%20these%20circumstances%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20BJP's%20challenge%20is%20how%20people%20have%20received%20populist%20programmes%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20-%20like%20free%20electricity%20up%20to%20100%20units%2C%20LPG%20gas%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20enhanced%20old%20age%20pension%20etc.%20Voters%20like%20freebies%2C%20though%20they%20also%20believe%20no%20matter%20who%20rules%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20freebies%20from%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20are%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20in%202014%2C%20there%20is%20no%20Modi%20wave%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Our%20government%20has%20rolled%20out%20several%20welfare%20schemes%20that%20have%20directly%20benefited%20people.%20In%20previous%20elections%2C%20when%20we%20-%20MLAs%20-%20used%20to%20tour%20our%20constituencies%2C%20people's%20mood%20was%20visible.%20This%20time%20people%20are%20welcoming%20us%20as%20they%20have%20seen%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20help%20improve%20their%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saleh%20Mohammad%2C%20Rajasthan%20Minister%20for%20Minority%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20are%20fed%20up%20of%20inflation%20and%20the%20youth%20are%20disillusioned%20due%20to%20unemployment%2C%20which%20are%20both%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20people%20understand%20it%20well.%20We%20are%20confident%20of%20forming%20the%20next%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20huge%20dissatisfaction%20among%20Congress%20MLAs.%20The%20party%20has%20conducted%20many%20electoral%20surveys%2C%20including%20one%20on%20popularity%20of%20its%20MLAs%20and%20other%20eligible%20candidates.%20Having%20made%20it%20unscathed%20this%20far%2C%20the%20Congress's%20prospects%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20wise%20selection%20of%20candidates%20based%20on%20winnability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProtests%20by%20Congress%20workers%20against%20some%20MLAs%20will%20compel%20the%20state%20and%20Delhi%20leadership%20to%20tread%20cautiously%20on%20distributing%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20bickering%20between%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20one-time%20deputy%20Sachin%20Pilot%20played%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20throughout%20the%20Congress's%20term%2C%20and%20may%20not%20be%20forgotten%20by%20the%20electorate.%20They%20may%20have%20called%20a%20fragile%20truce%20for%20now%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20people%20to%20forget%20the%20time%20and%20resources%20lost%20in%20managing%20the%20recurring%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gurjar%20and%20Meena%20belt%20of%20eastern%20Rajasthan%2C%20comprising%2024%20constituencies%20and%20accounting%20for%20five%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202018%20elections%20as%20Pilot%2C%20then%20state%20party%20president%2C%20was%20hopeful%20of%20becoming%20Chief%20Minister.%20However%2C%20seeing%20Pilot%2C%20a%20Gurjar%2C%20marginalised%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20community%20may%20opt%20for%20the%20BJP%20this%20time.%20The%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20rake%20up%20the%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(providing%20drinking%20water%20to%2013%20districts%20in%20east%20Rajasthan)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20delayed%20due%20to%20disputes%20between%20the%20state%20and%20central%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jats%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20OBC%20group%2C%20have%20never%20been%20happy%20with%20Gehlot.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%20of%20Nagaur%20MP%20Hanuman%20Beniwal%2C%20which%20is%20preparing%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20Jat-dominated%20constituencies.%20There%20are%20experts%20who%20believe%20that%20this%20Beniwal%20factor%20could%20damage%20the%20Congress%20more%20than%20the%20BJP.%20Should%20this%20happen%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20be%20in%20trouble%20in%20areas%20where%20it%20did%20very%20well%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20also%20wary%20of%20the%20new%20tribal%20party%20-%20Bharatiya%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP).%20BAP%20has%20emerged%20in%20place%20of%20the%20previous%20BTP%20(Bharatiya%20Tribal%20Party).%20BTP%20won%20two%20seats%20in%202018.%20BAP%20has%20done%20well%20in%20some%20tribal%20parts%20of%20southern%20Rajasthan%20in%20local%20elections.%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20had%20polled%20almost%205%20per%20cent%20votes%20in%202018.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20has%20been%20dormant%20of%20late%2C%20after%20its%20Rajasthan%20MLAs%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20is%20plagued%20by%20inter-party%20strife%20and%20so%20far%2C%20has%20not%20projected%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%20The%20party%20leadership%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20seems%20to%20tell%20the%20voters%20to%20trust%20the%20symbol%20and%20allow%20the%20party's%20democratic%20process%20to%20identify%20the%20next%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20fighting%20to%20stay%20relevant%20in%20the%20state%20but%20has%20been%20cold-shouldered%20by%20the%20national%20leadership.%20Raje's%20followers%20are%20angry%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20refused%20to%20project%20her%20as%20presumptive%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20has%20rejected%20many%20of%20her%20supporters%20as%20poll%20candidates.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20looking%20to%20foster%20a%20new%20leadership%20in%20the%20state%20and%20is%20fielding%20seven%20MPs%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20including%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Rathore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20banking%20on%20PM%20Modi%20to%20attract%20Hindu%20votes.%20The%20party%20has%20half%20a%20dozen%20leadership%20contenders%20-%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Shekhawat%2C%20leader%20of%20opposition%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Rathore%2C%20former%20state%20party%20president%20Satish%20Punia%20and%20Alwar%20MP%20Mahant%20Balak%20Nath.%20However%2C%20nobody%20has%20the%20appeal%20of%20Raje.%20Nor%20is%20the%20party%20leadership%20confident%20of%20projecting%20any%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhich%20boils%20down%20to%20an%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20Versus%20Who%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Gehlot%20looks%20stronger%20and%20taller%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20known%20challenger%20to%20confront%20him.%20That%20is%20somewhat%20similar%20to%20the%20Modi%20versus%20Who%20situation%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697725080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fklrp418_ashok-gehlot-1200_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fadvantage-ashok-gehlot-as-bjp-ducks-leadership-question-4497265