n%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20have%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20face%2C%20then%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20we%20need%20any%20other%20face%20in%20the%20state.%20Our%20first%20motive%20is%20to%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20after%20which%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20the%20CM%2C%20and%20we%20will%20stand%20with%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rathore%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERathore%20is%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20Congress%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAshok%20Gehlot%20is%20the%20same%20chief%20minister%20who%20once%20praised%20himself%20as%20the%20number%20one%20in%20the%20country%20and%20got%2021%20seats%20in%202013.%20Congress%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20an%20even%20bigger%20loss%20in%202013%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%20the%202013%20assembly%20election%2C%20Congress%20had%20won%2021%20seats%20out%20of%20200.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20have%20elected%20both%20parties.%20Rathore%20says%20that%20he%20believes%20it%20is%20now%20the%20time%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20be%20elected%20back.%20%E2%80%9CCM%20Gehlot%20says%20that%20this%20time%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20pattern%20will%20change%2C%20and%20Congress%20will%20continue%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20I%20agree%20with%20him%2C%20the%20pattern%20will%20change%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20be%20completely%20wiped%20out%20from%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasara%2C%20who%20is%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20lost%20the%20elections%20because%20it%20is%20giving%20tickets%20to%20MPs%20in%20Rajasthan.%20On%20this%2C%20Rathore%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi%20is%20the%20decision-maker%20in%20the%20party%2C%20and%20he%20decides%20which%20party%20worker%20will%20contest%20from%20which%20seat.%20We%20are%20standing%20with%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20What%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20Congress%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20cleared%20their%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%3F%20Even%20when%20the%20CM%20said%20in%20August%20that%20candidates%20must%20be%20known%20two%20months%20prior%20to%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJPs%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20came%20out%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20October.%20When%20can%20we%20expect%20the%20second%20list%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%2C%20our%20entire%20list%20of%20candidates%20will%20be%20out%2C%20and%20our%20party%20workers%20will%20be%20on%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20first%20list%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20given%20tickets%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20close%20aides%2C%20which%20disappointed%20some%20party%20workers%20who%20turned%20up%20at%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Jaipur.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20prominent%20faces%20and%20former%20ministers%20in%20her%20government.%20Narpat%20Singh%20from%20Vidyadhar%20Nagar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20late%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20had%20the%20portfolio%20of%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20replaced%20with%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Rajsamand.%20Rampal%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20from%20Jhotwara%20was%20replaced%20by%20Jaipur%20Rural%20MP%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Rathore.%20In%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20Rampal%20was%20Minister%20for%20Industries%2C%20Public%20Enterprises%2C%20DMIC%20%26amp%3B%20NRI%20Affairs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWere%20Raje%20and%20her%20aides%20being%20snubbed%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVasundhara%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20our%20leader%2C%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20will%20decide%20her%20role.%20When%20we%20have%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20then%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20we%20need%20any%20other%20face%20in%20the%20state.%20Our%20first%20motive%20is%20to%20win%20the%20elections%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaje%20was%20notably%20absent%20when%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20was%20present%20in%20Kota.%20Raje%20is%20also%20from%20the%20Hadoti%20region%2C%20and%20there%20are%2017%20seats%20in%20the%20region%20where%20BJP%20has%20a%20strong%20presence.%20Rathore%20rules%20out%20possibility%20of%20animosity%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20that.%20I%20also%20have%20to%20be%20there%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20election%20time%2C%20and%20we%20are%20all%20busy%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20change%20in%20Rajasthan%20if%20people%20bring%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20government%2C%20according%20to%20Rathore%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20many%20things%20will%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rathore.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20atmosphere%20of%20terror%20and%20plunder%20will%20change.%20We%20are%20making%20Sankalp%20Patra%2C%20which%20will%20be%20out%20soon.%20Our%20promises%20will%20be%20based%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20demands%20as%20we%20are%20visiting%20villages%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20noting%20down%20their%20demands%20so%20that%20we%20can%20put%20them%20on%20paper.%20Right%20now%2C%20in%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20every%20MLA%20of%20his%20is%20a%20mini-chief%20minister%20in%20their%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20success%20of%20double%20engine%20governments%20in%20states%20like%20Manipur%20which%20have%20seen%20so%20much%20violence%2C%20Rathore%20says%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewe%20should%20not%20compare%20things%20with%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20when%20asked%20as%20to%20why%20BJP%20is%20not%20declaring%20Ashok%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(ERCP)%20as%20a%20national%20project%2C%20Rathore%20cites%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20own%20failure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20objection%20to%20declaring%20it%20a%20national%20project.%20CM%20Gehlot%20had%20promised%20five%20years%20ago%20that%20he%20would%20resolve%20this%20problem%20on%20his%20own%2C%20and%20he%20failed.%20This%20government%20has%20no%20intention%20to%20fulfil%20this%20ERCP%20scheme.%20I%20remember%20when%20Kamal%20Nath%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20neighbouring%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20he%20had%20refused%20to%20give%20a%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20to%20Rajasthan%20for%20the%20project.%20If%20Mr.%20Gehlot%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20the%20people%2C%20he%20could%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20CWC%20and%20resolved%20the%20issue%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697722040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19181057%2FScreenshot-2023-10-19-at-6.10.49%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajendra-rathore-rajasthan-bjp-vasundhara-raje%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Vasundhara%20%5BRaje%5D%20ji%20is%20our%20leader%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20central%20leadership%20will%20decide%20her%20role%2C'%20said%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajendra-rathore-rajasthan-bjp-vasundhara-raje%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Indians%20Innovating%20With%20Millets%20to%20Make%20Them%20Appealing%20%26amp%3B%20Help%20Farmers%20Earn%20Big%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20a%20superfood%20that%20are%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20offer%20a%20plethora%20of%20benefits%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20grow%20them%2C%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20consume%20them.%20India%20is%20the%20top%20producer%20of%20these%20sustainable%20grains%20that%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20essential%20nutrients.%20This%20year%20is%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets%2C%20and%20the%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organisation%20(FAO)%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20is%20creating%20awareness%20about%20millets%20as%20affordable%20foods%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20healthy%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20millets%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20thrive%20in%20harsh%20growing%20conditions%20and%20are%20climate%20resilient.%20They%20require%20much%20less%20water%20than%20grains%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat.%20The%20FAO%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20They%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomical%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20becoming%20a%20boon%20to%20small%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20food%20grain%2C%20grown%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20were%20sidelined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20squarely%20back%20on%20how%20one%20can%20use%20these%20grains%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20farmers%20are%20switching%20back%20to%20growing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20change%20are%20Indians%20who%20are%20bringing%20millets%20back%20to%20the%20spotlight%20through%20their%20innovations.%20They%20are%20delivering%20millets%20in%20new%2C%20interesting%20ways%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20five%20Indians%20championing%20the%20humble%20grain%20through%20their%20startups%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%2C%20SS%20Bhavani%20Foods%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20583px)%20100vw%2C%20583px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22583%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veer%20Shetty%20Biradar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%20583w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-178x300.jpeg%20178w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-500x843.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-150x253.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Millet%20Man.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%20in%20Sangareddy%20district%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Veer%20Shetty%20Biradar%E2%80%99s%20life%20changed%20after%20a%20trip%20to%20Beed%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20in%202006.%20He