rarian%20village%20near%20Alibaug%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20millets%20were%20the%20staple%2C%20Sharmila%20Jain%20Oswal%20was%20well-acquainted%20with%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20grain%20and%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%20growing%20them.%20After%20a%20career%20as%20a%20lawyer%20in%20Canada%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20Pune%20in%202008%20and%20established%20an%20NGO%20called%20the%20Green%20Energy%20Foundation%20to%20help%20farmers%20revive%20water%20sources.%20She%20also%20helps%20them%20to%20implement%20smart%20farming%20methods%20including%20growing%20water-efficient%20crops%20like%20millet.%20She%20also%20co-founded%20%E2%80%98Gud%20Mom%E2%80%99%20with%20her%20son%20Shubham%2C%20which%20sells%20millet-based%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20helped%20over%201.5%20lakh%20farmers%20in%20five%20states%20since%20then%20through%20water%20management%20programmes%2C%20millet%20and%20vegetable%20cultivation%2C%20and%20capacity-building%20programmes%2C%20which%20has%20yielded%20a%20steady%20income%20for%20them.%20She%20urges%20farmers%20to%20grow%20millets%20in%20arid%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMillets%20are%20climate-resilient%2C%20carbon-neutral%20and%20eco-friendly.%20They%20require%20bare%20minimum%20water%2C%20making%20them%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20helped%20farmers%20diversify%20their%20crops%20and%20conserve%20water%20by%20teaching%20them%20how%20to%20cultivate%20millets%2C%20such%20as%20ragi%2C%20jowar%2C%20proso%20millet%2C%20and%20pearl%20millet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20vegetables%2C%20including%20exotic%20ones%20like%20zucchini.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gud%20Mom%E2%80%99%20sells%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet%20noodles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pasta%2C%20cookies%2C%20