0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-10-19%2Fasio-chief-says-no-reason-to-dispute-canada-india-spy-claim%2F102993480%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EABC%20New%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Australia%20Security%20Intelligence%20Organisation%20(ASIO)%20director%20general%20Mike%20Burgess%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20assessment%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20dispute%20what%20the%20Canadian%20government%20has%20said%20in%20this%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D%2C%20reiterating%20that%20Canada%20never%20taken%20Indian%20concerns%20on%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistani%20groups%20seriously.%20After%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20did%20the%20same%20to%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat.%20India%20also%20suspended%20visa%20operations%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20and%20also%20called%20on%20Canada%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20missions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20had%20explicitly%20linked%20the%20Canadian%20accusation%20to%20the%20five%20eyes%20intelligence%20network.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20shared%20intelligence%20among%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%20that%20helped%20lead%20Canada%20to%20making%20the%20statements%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20CTV%20News%2C%20a%20Canadian%20news%20channel.%20The%20US%20has%20repeatedly%20asked