3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmultiple%20countries%E2%80%9D%20had%20tried%20to%20interfere%20in%20Australian%20society%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2023%2Ffeb%2F14%2Faustralia-foils-iran-surveillance-plot-and-vows-to-bring-foreign-interference-into-the-light%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eciting%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20target%20an%20Iranian-Australian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ASIO%20head%20noted%20that%20in%20multi-cultural%20societies%2C%20there%20are%20often%20tensions%20associated%20from%20their%20home%20countries%20which%20find%20resonance%20in%20the%20diaspora.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20that%20plays%20out%20in%20society%2C%20you%20see%20protests%2C%20counter-protests%2C%20and%20sometimes%20there%E2%80%99s%20communal%20violence%20or%20spontaneous%20violence.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20nation%20state%20seeking%20to%20interfere%20and%20covertly%20or%20deceptively%20harm%20and%20intimidate%20people.%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20we%20see%20that%2C%20we%20will%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697720646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19182259%2FScreenshot-2023-10-19-at-6.22.52%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-spy-chief-mike-burgess-canada-nijjar-india-five-eyes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20ABC%20News%2C%20Australia%20Security%20Intelligence%20Organisation%20(ASIO)%20director%20general%20Mike%20Burgess%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20assessment%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-spy-chief-mike-burgess-canada-nijjar-india-five-eyes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22