ame-sex%20couples%20to%20marry%20speaks%20of%20there%20not%20existing%20a%20constitutional%20right%20to%20marry%2C%20of%20the%20need%20for%20judicial%20discipline%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20judiciary%20is%20not%20the%20correct%20forum%20to%20accommodate%20polyvocality%20in%20social%20issues.%20Vaguely%20intelligible%20obfuscation%20amounting%20to%20no%20more%20than%20the%20intellectualisation%20of%20the%20obscene%2C%20the%20rationalisation%20of%20the%20indefensible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20case%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20much%20simpler%20than%20all%20these%20justifications%20might%20lead%20the%20reader%20to%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20court%20to%20recognise%20a%20constitutional%20right%20to%20marry.%20The%20right%20to%20state-sanctioned%20marriage%20has%20already%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20same%20legislature%20the%20court%20otherwise%20seems%20comfortable%20deferring%20to%2C%20granted%20under%20the%20secular%20regime%20that%20is%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%20The%20primary%20issue%20before%20the%20court%2C%20by%20its%20own%20determination%2C%20was%20more%20limited%20%E2%80%93%20under%20that%20secular%20regime%2C%20once%20the%20right%20to%20marry%20is%20recognised%2C%20is%20it%20permissible%20for%20it%20to%20be%20extended%20to%20heterosexual%20couples%20but%20not%20to%20homosexual%20couples%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20question%2C%20then%2C%20was%20not%20whether%20%3Cem%3Ede%20novo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20same-sex%20couple%20can%20claim%20that%20the%20state%20must%20recognise%20their%20right%20to%20marry.%20Instead%2C%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20to%20marry%20was%20being%20asserted%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20state%20choosing%20to%20recognise%20some%20marriages%20and%20not%20others%3B%20of%20privileging%20some%20intimacies%20and%20not%20others%3B%20of%20saying%20some%20people%20can%20make%20end-of-life%20decisions%20for%20those%20they%20love%20and%20not%20others.%20The%20court%20was%20not%20to%20answer%20whether%20the%20Constitution%20granted%20a%20right%20to%20marry%3B%20it%20was%20to%20answer%20whether%20the%20Constitution%20permitted%20such%20a%20right%20to%20be%20granted%20selectively.%20The%20court%20was%20not%20asked%20to%20legislate%20and%20create%20an%20institution%20where%20none%20existed%3B%20it%20was%20asked%20to%20ensure%20that%20access%20to%20institutions%20that%20the%20legislature%20has%20already%20recognised%20was%20non-discriminatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Two%20Steps%20Forward%2C%20Three%20Steps%20Back%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Verdict%20on%20Marriage%20Equality%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftwo-steps-forward-three-steps-back-supreme-court-verdict-marriage-equality%5C%22%3ETwo%20Steps%20Forward%2C%20Three%20Steps%20Back%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Verdict%20on%20Marriage%20Equality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20fundamental%20task%2C%20the%20court%20has%20failed%20miserably.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20fallacy%20is%20perhaps%20best%20demonstrated%20by%20examining%20an%20analogy%20the%20majority%20opinion%20uses%20%E2%80%93%20it%20reasons%20that%20just%20because%20there%20exists%20a%20right%20to%20movement%20does%20not%20entitle%20a%20petitioner%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20and%20seek%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20specific%20network%20of%20roads.%20The%20analogy%20captures%20the%20very%20core%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20%E2%80%93%20the%20court%2C%20apparently%2C%20cannot%20by%20judicial%20diktat%20create%20laws%20or%20frameworks%20where%20none%20exist.%20That%20may%20well%20be%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20elude%20the%20court%20that%20a%20road%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20already%20been%20constructed%20here%3B%20it%20needed%20only%20to%20declare%20that%20no%20citizens%20could%20then%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEqually%20regrettable%20is%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20hand-wringing%20about%20how%20polyvocality%20cannot%20be%20accommodated%20in%20a%20judicial%20setting%2C%20and%20consequently%20the%20court%20is%20an%20inappropriate%20forum%20for%20making%20decisions%20about%20complex%20social%20issues%20like%20same-sex%20marriage.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20same-sex%20marriage%20is%20an%20issue%20which%20divides%20opinion%20in%20the%20socio-political%20realities%20of%20India.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20it%20is%20desirable%20that%20consensus%20on%20this%20issue%20be%20gradually%20built%20on%20the%20ground%20so%20that%20society%E2%80%99s%20acceptance%20of%20evolving%20norms%20is%20deepened.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20executive%20and%20legislature%20are%20better-placed%20than%20the%20judiciary%20to%20build%20and%20assess%20that%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20entitles%20the%20court%20to%20hold%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%20hostage%20to%20the%20building%20of%20that%20consensus.%20Consensus-building%20matters%20because%20it%20enables%20a%20deeper%20percolation%20of%20constitutional%20norms%2C%20not%20because%20public%20opinion%20exists%20outside%20of%20and%20beyond%20constitutional%20norms.%20State%20discrimination%20against%20a%20minority%20can%20never%20be%20recognised%20by%20majority%20fiat.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20conflicting%20opinions%20about%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20rights%20(or%2C%20worse%2C%20unanimity%20about%20trampling%20on%20them)%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20court%20is%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20that%20individual.%20It%20cannot%20and%20must%20not%20be%20to%20relegate%20that%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%20to%20the%20realm%20of%20policy%20debate%20simply%20because%20many%20others%20differ%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20those%20rights%2C%20and%20by%20so%20relegating%20them%20to%20the%20realm%20of%20policy%20debate%20concede%20the%20field%20utterly%20to%20the%20majoritarian%20impulses%20of%20the%20legislature.%20Polyvocality%20matters%20when%20debating%20the%20finer%20points%20of%20where%20public%20money%20should%20best%20be%20spent%3B%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20while%20recognising%20that%20the%20state%20is%20denying%20a%20group%20of%20individuals%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20judgement%20does%20not%20represent%20judicial%20restraint.%20It%20represents%20judicial%20abdication.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaustubh%20Chaturvedi%20is%20an%20advocate%20practising%20before%20various%20fora%20in%20Delhi.%20He%E2%80%99s%20an%20alumnus%20of%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%2C%20and%20can%20be%20contacted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akaustubhchaturvedi%40outlook.com%5C%22%3Ekaustubhchaturvedi%40outlook.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697713202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20110519%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-20-at-11.05.05-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-courts-marriage-equality-judgment-represents-judicial-abdication%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20was%20not%20asked%20to%20legislate%20and%20create%20an%20institution%20where%20none%20existed%3B%20it%20was%20asked%20to%20ensure%20that%20access%20to%20institutions%20that%20the%20legislature%20has%20already%20recognised%20was%20non-discriminatory.%20In%20this%20fundamental%20task%2C%20the%20court%20has%20failed%20miserably.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-courts-marriage-equality-judgment-represents-judicial-abdication%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Mannequin'%20arrested%20after%20Warsaw%20shop%20burglary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697712279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7D89%2Fproduction%2F_131473123_178-251523-002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67155928%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20arrest%2022-year-old%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20posing%20in%20a%20shop%20window%20before%20taking%20jewellery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1783%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67155928%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67155928.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67155928.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elgar%20Parishad%20Case%3A%20Since%20Evidence%20Tampering%20Not%20Ruled%20Out%2C%20Accused%20Want%20Chargesheets%20Quashed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113842%2FThe-Wire-42.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shoma%20Sen%20and%20Rona%20Wilson%2C%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20have%20alleged%20in%20their%20petition%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20that%20the%20prosecution%20violated%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%20in%20searching%20and%20seizing%20allegedly%20incriminating%20electronic%20documents%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20the%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20A.S.%20Gadkari%20and%20Justice%20Sharmila%20U.%20Deshmukh%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2017%2C%20to%20quash%20the%20chargesheets%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Anand%20Grover%20said%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20is%20relying%20on%2010%20documents%20that%20were%20recovered%20allegedly%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson.%20He%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20are%20not%20attachments%20and%20are%20unsigned%2C%20lacking%20probative%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20were%20neither%20written%20nor%20transmitted%20by%20Sen%20or%20Wilson%20and%20classified%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdigital%20hearsay%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fbombay-high-court-hears-petition-seeking-quashing-of-chargesheets-against-shoma-sen-and-rona-wilson%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrover%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F641904%2F%5C%22%3ESection%C2%A088A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20prohibits%20the%20presumption%20of%20the%20originator%20of%20electronic%20evidence.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Pune%20Police%20had%20failed%20to%20record%20the%20hash%20value%20of%20the%20devices%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20seizure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20hash%20value%20is%20a%20method%20widely%20known%20for%20the%20authentication%20of%20an%20electronic%20record%2C%20and%20police%20need%20to%20calculate%20the%20hash%20value%20when%20seizing%20electronic%20devices%20for%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20buttress%20his%20argument%2C%20Grover%20referred%20to%20Section%203%20of%20Information%20Technology%20(Security%20Procedure)%20Rules%2C%202004%2C%20which%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20electronic%20record%20shall%20be%C2%A0deemed%20to%20be%20a%20secure%20electronic%20record%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20Act%20if%20it%20has%20been%20authenticated%20by%20means%20of%20a%20secure%20digital%20signature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20tampering%20of%20the%20documents%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20given%20that%20Pune%20Police%20had%20sent%20the%20electronic%20device%20to%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20in%20Pune%20to%20ascertain%20its%20hash%20value.%20The%20mere%20sealing%20of%20electronic%20records%20at%20the%20place%20of%20seizure%20does%20not%20imply%20the%20security%20of%20data%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20Grover%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20electronic%20records%20that%20are%20not%20secure%20cannot%20presumed.%20To%20further%20his%20argument%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20in%202014%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F187283766%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EAnvar%20P.V.%20versus%20P.K.%20Basheer%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecase%20and%20added%20that%20given%20electronic%20evidence%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvolatile%20in%20nature%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tampered%20with%20easily%20without%20any%20signs%20or%20indications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20FSL%2C%20Pune%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20answer%20in%20its%20report%20whether%20the%20electronic%20device%20seized%20from%20Wilson%20had%20been%20tampered%20with.%20The%20clone%20copies%20of%20the%20seized%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20as%20required%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20%E2%80%93%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20to%20the%20accused%2C%20Grover%20informed%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20requests%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20by%20the%20accused%20from%20June%202018%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20the%20cloned%20copies%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20still%20pending%20before%20a%20special%20NIA%20court%2C%20Grover%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20arguments%20of%20Grover%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson%2C%20assume%20significance%20as%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20severe%20malpractice%20by%20investigating%20authorities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medianama.com%2F2023%2F10%2F223-anand-grover-bhima-koregaon-seized-devices-security%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMedianama%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Arsenal%20Consulting%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20traces%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%20were%20found%20on%20Wilson%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20and%20also%20said%20he%20had%20received%20phishing%20emails%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20actor%E2%80%9D%20between%202013%20and%202014%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-researchers-claim-link-between-pune-police-and-hacking-campaign-against-bhima-koreagon-accused%5C%22%3ESentinelOne%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleged%20that%20hacking%20groups%20were%20used%20to%20target%20Wilson%E2%80%99s%20electronic%20devices.%20Even%20Amnesty%20International%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it%20had%20found%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20Pune%20Police%20had%20hacked%20the%20emails%20of%20various%20arrested%20activists%2C%20including%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711445000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113842%2FThe-Wire-42.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-case-since-evidence-tampering-not-ruled-out-accused-want-chargesheets-quashed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoma%20Sen%20and%20Rona%20Wilson%20petitioned%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20alleging%20that%20norms%20were%20violated%20in%20searching%20and%20seizing%20electronic%20documents%20from%20them.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-case-since-evidence-tampering-not-ruled-out-accused-want-chargesheets-quashed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20follows%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20Israel%20to%20show%20support%20as%20bombs%20hit%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711262