r%20Ibrahim%20revolted%20against%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20He%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20%E2%80%98like-minded%E2%80%99%20people%20in%20JD(S)%20on%20Monday%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdefying-jds-leadership-karnataka-unit-chief-says-party-not-in-favour-of-alliance-with-bjp%5C%22%3Eannounce%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20core%20committee%20to%20submit%20a%20memorandum%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20should%20not%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20that%20his%20faction%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Coriginal%20one%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1714918092458086403%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1714918092458086403%257Ctwgr%255Ec0d3352241b134737f90b7160596fe940ea839b2%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hindustantimes.com%252Findia-news%252Fcm-ibrahim-expelled-as-karnataka-jd-s-president-101697702252012.html%5C%22%3Ereporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20strengthen%20the%20party%2C%20our%20national%20president%20today%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20dissolve%20the%20old%20unit%20and%20announced%20the%20ad-hoc%20committee%20in%20my%20leadership%E2%80%A6%20Naturally%2C%20it%20will%20be%20communicated%20to%20him%20(CM%20Ibrahim)%E2%80%A6My%20responsibility%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20party%E2%80%A6My%20concentration%20is%20to%20develop%20my%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIbrahim%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20the%20BJP%20then%20let%20them%20go%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20asking%20them%20(Gowda%20and%20Kumaraswamy)%20not%20to%20go.%20If%20they%20go%20then%20we%20cannot%20bind%20them.%20Regarding%20(JD-S)%20MLAs%2C%20please%20wait%20and%20see%20who%2C%20how%20many%2C%20and%20where%20these%20MLAs%20will%20take%20a%20decision.%20We%20will%20intimate%20you%20w