20%5Bdirect%20messages%5D%20and%20requests%20from%20both%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20talk%20and%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20listen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overwhelming%20response%20made%20Raj%20realise%20that%20his%20initiative%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20forum%20of%20listeners.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20started.%20Today%20our%20non-profit%20is%20around%20600%20listeners%20strong%20who%20are%20all%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20or%20listeners%20and%20the%20people%20who%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20are%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELending%20a%20compassionate%20ear%20to%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20a%20person%20can%20become%20a%20listener%2C%20Raj%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stories%20and%20incidents%20that%20people%20share%20can%20be%20quite%20taxing%20and%20overwhelming.%20This%20is%20why%20every%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20listener%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20small%20evaluation%2C%20conducted%20by%20psychologists%20and%20therapists%20who%20collaborate%20with%20us.%20Once%20the%20volunteers%20are%20cleared%20by%20the%20therapist%2C%20we%20let%20them%20in%20our%20army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20Raj%20has%20amassed%20a%20following%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20on%20Instagram.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESo%20far%2C%20Raj%20has%20amassed%20a%20following%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20on%20Instagram.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Raj%20Dagwar%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20it%20was%20just%20something%20that%20I%20did%2C%20he%20says%2C%20but%20now%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSessions%20are%20held%20absolutely%20free%20of%20cost%20in%20both%20online%20and%20offline%20formats.%20Anyone%20can%20come%20and%20tell%20us%20their%20story%2C%20and%20we%20simply%20listen.%20If%20the%20listener%20feels%20that%20the%20person%20needs%20professional%20help%2C%20they%20refer%20them%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F79625%2Fritu-nakra-ananya-hearing-disability-therapist-films%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etherapists%20or%20psychologists%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20government%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAteesh%20Anna%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20volunteer%20for%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20about%20the%20initiative%20through%20Instagram%20and%20was%20very%20intrigued.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20such%20an%20amazing%20movement.%20I%20have%20been%20volunteering%20with%20them%20from%20Raipur%20for%20the%20past%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharing%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20incidents%20as%20a%20listener%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20old%20woman%20who%20saw%20my%20sign%20and%20walked%20up%20to%20me.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20have%20so%20many%20stories%2C%20you%20will%20need%20all%20day%E2%80%99.%20I%20readily%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Come%2C%20let%20us%20sit%E2%80%99.%20She%20spoke%20to%20me%20for%2048%20minutes%20and%20told%20me%20how%20lonely%20she%20feels%20at%20home%2C%20now%20that%20her%20kids%20are%20all%20settled%20far%20away.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20talking%20to%20me%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20talking%20to%20her%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20my%20day!%20Isolation%20among%20seniors%20is%20a%20topic%20that%20is%20rarely%20discussed.%20They%20mostly%20suffer%20alone%20and%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20I%20could%20be%20her%20friend%20that%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Raj%20has%20lost%20count%20of%20the%20number%20of%20stories%20he%E2%80%99s%20heard.%20%E2%80%9COne%20common%20thread%20runs%20through%20all%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20isolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tell%20them%20that%20even%20I%20once%20believed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20feeling%20depressed.%20But%20with%20the%20right%20support%20system%2C%20you%20can%20overcome%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzYGh6oYCS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzYGh6oYCS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%