d%20cabinets%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20elated%20artist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173413%2Fprayagraj-kumbh-2019-street-art-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20pieces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20mosaic%20and%20wood%20art%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20cheap.%20Also%2C%20since%20only%20the%20two%20of%20them%20handle%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%2C%20they%20cannot%20make%20products%20in%20large%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20are%20two%20other%20people%20in%20their%20workshop%20who%20help%20with%20the%20mosaic%20works%20along%20with%20three%20freelancing%20carpenters%20and%20polishers%20for%20the%20woodwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20arts%20from%20their%20studio%20start%20at%20Rs%202%2C000-2%2C500%20per%20square%20foot%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20design.%20The%20price%20of%20a%20driftwood%20centre%20table%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2018%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20wood.%20Mosaic%20garden%20tables%2C%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%2C%20cost%20Rs%2012%2C500.%20Floor%20lamps%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%207%2C000-10%2C000.%20Planters%20range%20from%20Rs%205%2C000-15%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYohann%20has%20a%20residence-cum-studio%20in%20Bandra%20where%20clients%20can%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20products.%20The%20company%20gets%20orders%20from%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20our%20clientele%20is%20outside%20Mumbai.%20Our%20products%20are%20large%20and%20meant%20for%20large%20spaces.%20Around%2060%20percent%20of%20our%20pieces%20are%20custom-made%20while%2040%20percent%20is%20from%20an%20inventory.%20We%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20grow%20the%20business%20through%20projects%20to%20do%20up%20villas%20and%20homes%20by%20collaborating%20with%20interior%20designers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20537px)%20100vw%2C%20537px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-table%20made%20with%20using%20a%20piece%20of%20driftwood.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566.jpg%20537w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-262x300.jpg%20262w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-500x572.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-150x172.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20side-table%20made%20with%20using%20a%20piece%20of%20driftwood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20unique%20products%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20mosaic%20pieces%20are%20indeed%20eye-catching%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20driftwood%20tables%20and%20other%20wares%20that%20are%20equally%20beautiful%20too.%20Driftwood%20is%20basically%20the%20wood%20that%20has%20been%20washed%20ashore%20onto%20a%20beach%20from%20the%20sea%2C%20lake%20or%20a%20river.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDriftwood%20as%20well%20as%20upcycled%20wood%20come%20with%20a%20history.%20The%20character%2C%20texture%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20shape%20work%20as%20an%20inspiration%20for%20us.%20It%20requires%20a%20keen%20eye%2C%20and%20an%20active%20imagination%20to%20visualise%20and%20conceptualise%20the%20potential%20of%20every%20piece.%20And%20each%20one%20is%20different.%20Some%20make%20great%20lamps%2C%20some%20ingenious%20tabletops%2C%20some%20rustic%20benches.%20They%20can%20be%20used%20within%20the%20home%20and%20outdoors%20too.%C2%A0No%20two%20pieces%20are%20the%20same%20and%20the%20challenge%20is%20always%20to%20create%20something%20different.%20It%20is%20the%20joy%20and%20immense%20satisfaction%20of%20creating%20art%20from%20waste%20that%20drives%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naomi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDriftwood%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20rigorous%20process%20before%20it%20can%20be%20worked%20with.%20It%20involves%20scrubbing%20and%20cleaning%20the%20piece%2C%20bleaching%20it%20over%20a%20period%20of%20weeks%20to%20remove%20the%20insects%20as%20well%20as%20lighten%20the%20wood%C2%A0tones.%20Then%20it%20is%20protected%20from%20termites%20and%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20to%20dry%20thoroughly%2C%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20entire%20day%20is%20spent%20in%20my%20workshop%2C%20especially%20if%20we%20have%20hard%20deadlines.%20At%20times%2C%20day%20creeps%20into%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20even%20forget%20to%20eat.%20I%20hire%20more%20hands%20on%20a%20daily%20wage%20basis%20if%20I%20need%20extra%20assistance.%20While%20I%20lay%20the%20creative%20groundwork%20for%20a%20piece%2C%20the%20machine%20work%20is%20handled%20by%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20clients%20like%20The%20Dignity%20Foundation%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20who%20got%20a%20piece%20made%20for%20their%20newest%20project%20in%20Neral%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20the%20LV%20Prasad%20eye%20hospital%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20or%20the%20three%20murals%20they%20made%20for%20the%20Santori%20Resort%20at%20Mulshi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20studio%20keeps%20busy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20business%20in%20my%20fifties%2C%20much%20against%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20advice%20and%20with%20many%20negative%20comments%20from%20sceptics%20and%20naysayers.%20Some%20people%20felt%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20re